	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia filii dei tecum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum noster <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1137" cert="high">Chunradus Functius</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l335" cert="high">Mylhusanę</placeName> minister ecclesię, a nundinis <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentoratensibus</placeName> properans domum apud me pernoctaret significassetque se brevi ad te iturum, hasce ad te dare volui, humanissime <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>, atque oro, si tua Repetitio in <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentium</persName> solem videre nequit, remittatur matronę; habebit spelaeum, quo abdatur.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3988">Ioannem Wolffium</persName> sedulo monebis<foreign xml:lang="el">κθκλοπαιδιαν</foreign> quamprimum et fęliciter absolvere, ut scholae aliquando pręficiatur reique publicę sementarium instituat etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alter eius collega <persName type="citizen_name">Regius</persName> Basileę, ut audio, hęrebit suspenso studio et artibus postergatis.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Constans rumor et suspitio dissipatur, cum habitet apud benignam, aut si mavis, si verum est, quod fertur, malignam domini <persName type="citizen_name">Thomę</persName> bonę memorie <persName type="auto_name">Girfalckum</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">vielleicht - falckn für - falckensis</note> viduam duxisse uxorem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si verum, studium illius habebit stultum in supino.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nostrum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1137" cert="high">Chunradum</persName> tuę pietati commendo, qui referet nostrum statum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale et saluta fratres omnes, d. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherum</persName>, tuos generos ac familiam, ac orate pro capulari sene.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die 18. iulii 65.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p1010" cert="high">Erbius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viro pietate, eruditione sanctaque vita eximio d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrycho Bullingero</persName>, syncero theologo inclytęque urbis Tigurinę antistiti fideli, suo fratri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
